name: Saber 2
Lore: 'TIE interceptor flown by Major Phennir. Assigned to protect Avenger at the Battle of Endor. Responsible for the logistics of Saber Squadron.',
Text: 'May add 1 pilot. When Phennir piloting, immune to attrition < 4 and adds 1 to forfeit of each other Saber Squadron pilot in same battle.',
